questions.quote: Why not? You'll feel better! I'll feel better, and you know you want to. I can see it in your eyes.

Yeah, definitely, definitely. Ok, what do you wanna see first?
No way! If anything you've gotta let me win! My wife thinks I'm a wimp!
Look guys, when I'm with her it's-it's-it's like she brings this-this-this great side out of me. I mean I-I-I love her, y'know?
I-I-I saw you on stage talking to that beautiful woman, y'know Sarah?
No-no, oh, I'm fine with the age thing y'know, until it starts sticking it's tongue down my little brother's throat!
